com.pillar

Class VendingMachineTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pillar.VendingMachineTests

  • public class VendingMachineTests
extends java.lang.Object
    The following tests ensure the vending machine is able to function correctly. These tests ensure the machine is able to read coins correctly, display output, dispense change, and keep track of inventory.
